<div class="ability explanation">
	<div class="title">Abilities</div>
	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/67e1d7b7a658af6624ecd3c0af03e0d52.png"></span><span>Waterwyrm's Guidance II</span></dt><dd><div>Grants Emile a dragondrive gauge and changes<br>the shapeshift button into a dragondrive button.<br>Tapping this button activates Emile's dragondrive,<br>consumes some of the dragondrive gauge, and<br>performs a special attack. Emile's dragondrive<br>ends immediately after this attack.<br><br>Also, grants Emile an ego gauge with three<br>charges. The ego gauge fills when standard<br>attacks, dash attacks, and force strikes<br>connect with enemies.<br><br>In addition, grants Emile four more skill points<br>for equipping shared skills and increases<br>his skill gauge fill rate by 40%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/f3503b7c11dab7e6111611cb63f010c32.png"></span><span>Immeasurable Majesty II</span></dt><dd><div>Reduces susceptibility to burning and stun by 100%.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/318c94807552d34eb43eebac3f21952f2.png"></span><span>The Great and Powerful Emperor Emile II</span></dt><dd><div>Increases damage dealt by shared skills<br>by 150%. Shared skills that deal damage<br>will also inflict frostbite.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>・The stats shown here do not include increases or decreases due to abilities and represent the adventurer at level 80 with 50 mana nodes unlocked, not the stats when first obtained.</div><div><br></div><div>■Regarding Gala Emile&#39;s Abilities The Great and Powerful Emperor Emile I and II<br>The effects of Gala Emile&#39;s abilities The Great and Powerful Emperor Emile I and II will also apply to shared skills and weapon skills in the Kaleidoscape.<br><br></div><div>Notes:</div><div>1. For more information about summoning, tap Summon on the in-game footer menu, then select Showcase Info and check the Details tab.</div><div>2. An Alberian Battle Royale skin for the adventurer featured in this summon showcase will go on sale and will cost fewer items to unlock. Note that some adventurers do not have adventurer skins.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1643522400,update_time1643766262